---
layout: base.njk
title: Ски услуги — TES Borovets
---
{% set lang = lang or "bg" %}
{% set t = i18n[lang] %}
{% set prefix = "" if lang == "bg" else "/en" %}
{% set serviceId = "ski" %}
{% set currentService = client.services | selectattr("id", "equalto", serviceId) | first %}

<!-- Breadcrumb -->
<nav class="breadcrumb" aria-label="breadcrumb">
  <div class="container">
    <ol class="breadcrumb-list">
      <li><a href="{{ prefix }}/">{{ t.breadcrumb_home }}</a></li>
      <li>
        <span class="bc-sep" aria-hidden="true">›</span>
        <a href="{{ prefix }}/services/">{{ t.breadcrumb_services }}</a>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="bc-sep" aria-hidden="true">›</span>
        <span class="bc-current">{{ currentService.name }}</span>
      </li>
    </ol>
  </div>
</nav>

<!-- Hero -->
<section class="hero hero-sm" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2C5274 0%, #102A43 100%);">
  <div class="container hero-content">
    <span class="eyebrow" style="color: var(--color-accent-300);">{{ t.breadcrumb_services }}</span>
    <div style="font-size: 3rem; margin-bottom: var(--space-3);" aria-hidden="true">⛷️</div>
    <h1>{{ currentService.name }}</h1>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Content -->
<section>
  <div class="container">
    <div style="max-width: var(--container-md);">
      {% if lang == "bg" %}
        <p class="lead">Наемане на ски и сноуборд оборудване, уроци за начинаещи и напреднали, съдействие за ски пас и групови преходи.</p>
        <div class="process-steps" style="margin-top: var(--space-7);">
          <div class="process-step">
            <div class="process-step-content">
              <h4>Избор на оборудване</h4>
              <p>Ски, сноуборд, ски обувки — подбираме спрямо ниво и ръст. Налично за всички възрасти.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="process-step">
            <div class="process-step-content">
              <h4>Уроци с инструктор</h4>
              <p>Индивидуални или групови уроци с опитни инструктори — от първи стъпки до напреднала техника.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="process-step">
            <div class="process-step-content">
              <h4>Ски пас и писти</h4>
              <p>Съдействие при закупуване на ски пас. Боровец разполага с 25 км писти от всички нива.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      {% else %}
        <p class="lead">Ski and snowboard equipment rental, lessons for beginners and advanced, ski pass assistance and group transfers.</p>
        <div class="process-steps" style="margin-top: var(--space-7);">
          <div class="process-step">
            <div class="process-step-content">
              <h4>Equipment Selection</h4>
              <p>Skis, snowboards, boots — fitted to your level and height. Available for all ages.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="process-step">
            <div class="process-step-content">
              <h4>Lessons with an Instructor</h4>
              <p>Private or group lessons with experienced instructors — from first steps to advanced technique.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="process-step">
            <div class="process-step-content">
              <h4>Ski Pass & Slopes</h4>
              <p>Assistance purchasing a ski pass. Borovets has 25 km of slopes for all levels.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      {% endif %}

      <p style="margin-top: var(--space-6); color: var(--color-neutral-500); font-size: var(--text-sm);">{{ t.service_pricing_note }}</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Contact -->
<section class="section-alt">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>{{ t.contact_methods_title }}</h2>
    {% include "contact-methods.njk" %}
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Related Services -->
<section>
  <div class="container">
    <h2>{{ t.service_related_label }}</h2>
    <div class="services-grid" style="margin-top: var(--space-6);">
      {% set showDesc = false %}
      {% for service in client.services %}
        {% if service.id != serviceId %}
          {% include "service-card.njk" %}
        {% endif %}
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
